short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Logs into a roblox account with the cookie on your clipboard, made by ADAM#8888

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension makes it easier to log into your Roblox account with a cookie on your clipboard, rather than using EditThisCookie and manually replacing the cookie.
